description:
Supported Platforms:
• NETStandard
• UWP
• XamariniOS
• XamarinAndroid
• NETFramework


Rapidly develop robust, accurate, and extremely fast OCR and Forms Recognition and Processing applications that extract text and data. OCR Technology converts document images to text-searchable and editable formats such as PDF, PDF/A, DOC, DOCX, XML, and XPS. Supports character sets for more than 40 languages.  

This package includes English, Spanish, French, Italian, and German. For more languages, see the Leadtools.Ocr.Languages.* packages.

Forms recognition and processing technology detects and processes unstructured and semi-structured documents such as bubble forms, invoices, applications/tax forms, checks, passports, driver's licenses, business cards, and credit cards. LEADTOOLS Forms uses an advanced combination of OCR, OMR, ICR, barcode, and intelligent image processing techniques, image cleanup and more to automate the extraction of text from complex documents.  

This is just a small part of a large technology offering called LEADTOOLS. To see all that LEADTOOLS has to offer, go to https://www.leadtools.com



Example Projects:
• OCR - https://bitly.im/leadtools_ocr
• Forms Recognition and Processing - https://bitly.im/leadtools_forms
• All - https://bitly.im/leadtools_all
